{"tha-ap262:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap262:0.2":"Thomakavagga ","tha-ap262:0.3":"Aggapupphiyattheraapadana ","tha-ap262:1.1":"“Suvannavannam sambuddham, ","tha-ap262:1.2":"Nisinnam pabbatantare; ","tha-ap262:1.3":"Obhasayantam ramsena, ","tha-ap262:1.4":"Sikhinam sikhinam yatha. ","tha-ap262:2.1":"Aggajam pupphamadaya, ","tha-ap262:2.2":"upagacchim naruttamam; ","tha-ap262:2.3":"Pasannacitto sumano, ","tha-ap262:2.4":"buddhassa abhiropayim. ","tha-ap262:3.1":"Ekattimse ito kappe, ","tha-ap262:3.2":"yam pupphamabhipujayim; ","tha-ap262:3.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap262:3.4":"buddhapujayidam phalam. ","tha-ap262:4.1":"Pancavisatikappamhi, ","tha-ap262:4.2":"ahosi amitogato; ","tha-ap262:4.3":"Sattaratanasampanno, ","tha-ap262:4.4":"cakkavatti mahabbalo. ","tha-ap262:5.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap262:5.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap262:5.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap262:6.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma aggapupphiyo thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap262:7.1":"Aggapupphiyattherassapadanam dasamam. ","tha-ap262:8.1":"Thomakavaggo chabbisatimo. ","tha-ap262:9.1":"Tassuddanam ","tha-ap262:10.1":"Thomakekasanacitakam, ","tha-ap262:10.2":"campako sattapatali; ","tha-ap262:10.3":"Panadhi manjari pannam, ","tha-ap262:10.4":"kutido aggapupphiyo; ","tha-ap262:10.5":"Gathayo ganita cettha, ","tha-ap262:10.6":"ekatalisameva cati. "}